---
import MizuLayout from '@/layouts/MizuLayout.astro'
---

<MizuLayout
  title="Careers | Pixelated Empathy"
  description="Join our mission to revolutionize mental health training through AI technology. We're building a team passionate about making a difference."
>
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background effects -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full z-0 pointer-events-none"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 mix-blend-screen animate-pulse"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 mix-blend-screen animate-pulse [animation-delay:1000ms]"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white"
        >
          Join Our Mission
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          We're building the future of mental health training. If you're
          passionate about AI, healthcare, and making a real difference, we'd
          love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Company Values -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Innovation First</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            We're pushing the boundaries of what's possible with AI in mental
            health training, using cutting-edge technology to solve real
            problems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Impact Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Every line of code, every feature, every decision is made with the
            goal of improving mental health outcomes and training quality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Continuous Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            We believe in growth, both personal and professional. You'll work
            with cutting-edge technology and learn from challenges every day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Open Positions -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12"
        >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">We're Growing</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            While we don't have specific positions open right now, we're always
            looking for exceptional people who share our vision. If you're
            passionate about:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>AI/ML Engineering and Research</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Full-Stack Development (TypeScript, Python, Rust)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Mental Health Technology and Clinical Applications</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Product Design and UX for Healthcare</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Security and Privacy Engineering</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We'd love to hear from you. Send us a message and let's start a
            conversation.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25 hover:shadow-primary-500/40 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            Get in Touch
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Why Join Us -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">
          Why Join Pixelated Empathy?
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
              Meaningful Work
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Your work directly impacts how mental health professionals are
              trained, potentially improving outcomes for thousands of patients.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
              Cutting-Edge Technology
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Work with the latest AI models, homomorphic encryption, and modern
              web technologies in a production environment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
              Flexible & Remote-Friendly
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              We believe in work-life balance and support remote work. Focus on
              results, not hours in an office.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
              Early-Stage Impact
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Join at the ground floor and help shape the direction of the
              company. Your ideas and contributions will have real impact.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MizuLayout>
